1-)Install  wikipedia 
'pip install wikipedia' #Open up your command prompt(cmd) or terminal and type this
Warning!:
If 'pip install wikipedia' does not work just type 'python -m pip install wikipedia'   #definitely works
2-) Install SpeechRecognition 
'pip install SpeechRecognition'   #Open up your command prompt(cmd) or terminal and type this
Warning!:
If 'pip install SpeechRecognition' does not work just type 'python -m pip install SpeechRecognition'   #definitely works
3-) Install pyttsx3
'pip install pyttsx3'    #Open up your command prompt(cmd) or terminal and type this
Warning!:
If 'pip install pyttsx3' does not work just type 'python -m pip install pyttsx3'   #definitely works
4-) Install DateTime
'pip install DateTime' #Open up your command prompt(cmd) or terminal and type this
Warning!:
If 'pip install DateTime' does not work just type 'python -m pip install DateTime'   #definitely works
